sts():\n70\t        scores[\"file_created\"] = 0.0\n71\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 0.0\n72\t        scores[\"lag_rate_positive\"] = 0.0\n73\t        scores[\"etf_queried\"] = 0.0\n74\t        scores[\"fundamentals_checked\"] = 0.0\n75\t        return scores\n76\t\n77\t    scores[\"file_created\"] = 1.0\n78\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\n79\t\n80\t    no_result_phrases = [\"无符合\", \"没有\", \"none\"]\n81\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\n82\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0\n83\t        scores[\"lag_rate_positive\"] = 1.0\n84\t    else:\n85\t        has_code = bool(re.search(r'3\\d{5}', content))\n86\t        has_etf = bool(re.search(r'15\\d{4}', content))  # ETF codes start with 15xxxx\n87\t        scores[\"valid_format\"] = 1.0 if (has_code and has_etf) else (0.5 if has_code else 0.0)\n88\t\n89\t        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\n90\t                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\"#\") and \"代码\" not in l]\n91\t        records = []\n92\t        for line in lines:\n93\t            parts = re.split(r'[,\\s\\t]+', line)\n94\t            if len(parts) >= 7:\n95\t                try:\n96\t                    stock_ret = float(parts[2].replace('%', ''))\n97\t                    etf_ret = float(parts[3].replace('%', ''))\n98\t                    lag_rate = float(parts[4].replace('%', ''))\n99\t                    records.append((stock_ret, etf_ret, lag_rate))\n100\t                except:\n101\t                    pass\n102\t\n103\t        valid_lag = [r for r in records if r[2] > 0 and r[0] < r[1]]\n104\t        scores[\"lag_rate_positive\"] = 1.0 if len(valid_lag) == len(records) and len(records) > 0 else (0.5 if len(valid_lag) > 0 else 0.0)\n105\t\n106\t    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\n107\t    etf_codes = [\"159929\", \"159813\", \"159642\", \"etf\"]\n108\t    scores[\"etf_queried\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in etf_codes) else 0.0\n109\t    scores[\"fundamentals_checked\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\n110\t        [\"roe\", \"pe\", \"净资产收益率\", \"市盈率\"]) else 0.0\n111\t\n112\t    return scores\n113\t```\n114\t\n115\t---\n116\t\n117\t## LLM Judge Rubric\n118\t\n119\t### Criterion 1: ETF数据获取与上涨趋势识别（Weight: 25%）\n120\t\n121\t**Score 1.0**: 正确获取了至少3个行业ETF的数据，涨幅和均线趋势判断正确（20日涨幅>8%且5日>20日均线），筛选出了上涨ETF。\n122\t**Score 0.75**: 获取了2-3个ETF，趋势判断基本正确。\n123\t**Score 0.5**: 只获取了1个ETF，或ETF代码使用错误但方向正确。\n124\t**Score 0.25**: ETF数据获取有明显问题。\n125\t**Score 0.0**: 未获取ETF数据。\n126\t\n127\t### Criterion 2: 成分股滞涨识别逻辑（Weight: 35%）\n128\t\n129\t**Score 1.0**: 正确获取或近似成分股，滞涨定义（<ETF涨幅50%）正确实现，滞涨率计算公式准确，正确建立个股与对应ETF的关联。\n130\t**Score 0.75**: 滞涨识别基本正确，成分股用行业股票近似但覆盖率不足。\n131\t**Score 0.5**: 滞涨阈值有偏差（如<ETF涨幅的70%），或成分股获取有问题。\n132\t**Score 0.25**: 滞涨识别逻辑有根本性错误。\n133\t**Score 0.0**: 未实现滞涨识别。\n134\t\n135\t### Criterion 3: 基本面与技术面验证（Weight: 40%）\n136\t\n137\t**Score 1.0**: PE>0且ROE>8%的基本面筛选正确，MACD将金叉或刚金叉（含距离缩小判断）且KDJ<50的技术面信号检测准确，两类验证均有合理实现。\n138\t**Score 0.75**: 基本面验证正确，技术面验证有简化（如只检查MACD金叉，未检查KDJ）。\n139\t**Score 0.5**: 只实现了基本面或技术面其中一类验证。\n140\t**Score 0.25**: 两类验证均有实现但有明显错误。\n141\t**Score 0.0**: 未实现基本面和技术面验证。\n142\t\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b9a72a17-46e7-40a2-a50a-1eb55e3b3526","uuid":"2250cff4-a28b-482a-b48b-51ff4fc801c7","timestamp":"2026-04-16T10:59:21.043Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/tomato/Documents/potato/project/YFD/yfd-agent-consensus/results/agent_consensus_batch/default_run/task_34_etf_constituent_arbitrage/consensus/claudecode/task.md","content":"---\nid: task_34_etf_constituent_arbitrage\nname: ETF成分股滞涨套利机会识别\ncategory: etf_constituent_arbit